videos.description: Gonzaga's Corey Kispert swishes home a 3-pointer and reacts by staring down his hand on his way back on defense.

videos.description: Off a missed shot, Southern Miss grabs an offensive rebound, but Filip Petrusev denies the putback attempt with a big block.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Petrusev gets emphatic rejection
